This allows us to identify a ﬁnite subset Wdof the lattice Zd, such that any smooth Fano d-polytope is isomorphic to one whose vertices are contained in Wd(theorem 3.6).

For instance, http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns# is prexed as rdf: .
